PublicRemarks: This 2-bedroom, 2-bathroom condo boasts an open-concept layout that creates a wonderfully spacious and inviting living space. Step out to your private walk-out balcony, an idyllic oasis where you can unwind, enjoy scenic views, and breathe in the fresh air after a long day.  5 minutes from the 407ETR, you'll also find groceries, shopping centres, restaurants, a theatre, the Viva bus terminal, Langstaff GO station, parks, schools, and a vibrant community centre all within a stone's throw. PublicRemarks: Built by Aspen Ridge Homes this contemporary style condo will tick all the boxes. Nine foot ceilings and to the spacious feel of this 1011 sq ft. corner unit. Large windows with custom blinds feature light filtering and blackout option, let in an abundance of natural light. This open concept layout has a combined living and dining area overlooking the functional kitchen with granite counters, stainless steel appliances and a movable island. The primary suite has a 3pc ensuite with a walk-in shower and a walk-in closet. A second bedroom has his and hers closets with sliding doors and large windows. The 4pc bathroom and utility closet with ensuite laundry complete the interior space. With walk-outs to the balcony from every room you can relax and enjoy the pleasant views from your private outdoor space. Leave the car at home, you are in walking distance to the GO station, Shopper's Drug Mart, and many other local amenities. Parks and schools close by. (33486659)
